Cathoris tells you 'have you ever seen one of those electric shock machines?'
Cathoris tells you 'you hold on to these 2 metal handles.'
Cathoris tells you 'and the voltage slowly goes up'
Cathoris tells you 'you see who can hold on for longest.'
